headline: As Economies Face Pressures to Adapt Pension Systems, 2025 Mercer CFA Institute Global Pension Index Outlines Principles to Balance Retirees’ Needs and National Interests
summary: NEW YORK, October 15, 2025--Mercer, a business of Marsh McLennan (NYSE: MMC) and a global leader in helping clients realize their investment objectives, shape the future of work and enhance health and retirement outcomes for their people, and CFA Institute, the global association of investment professionals, today released the 17th annual Mercer CFA Institute Global Pension Index (MCGPI).
